text: Balagach-Kul () is a rural locality (a village) in Kakrybashevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 48 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Tuymazy, 4 km from Kakrybashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Balagach-Kul
